s through each step of the process, including patient positioning, maintaining hygiene, and ensuring patient comfort and dignity.  \n\n# Learning Objectives:  \n- Remembering the steps and protocols for bedpan assistance \n- Understanding the importance of patient comfort and dignity during the process \n- Applying the correct techniques for positioning and assisting patients \n- Analyzing the situation to provide appropriate care tailored to individual patient needs \n-  Evaluating the effectiveness of the assistance provided and making necessary adjustments \n- Creating a comfortable and respectful environment for patients requiring bedpan assistance.  \n\nThis comprehensive approach ensures CNAs are well-prepared to perform bedpan assistance effectively and compassionately in real-world clinical settings. ", "short_description": "Designed to train CNAs in providing proper bedpan assistance through interactive, hands-on practice."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.holopundits.com/privacy-policy.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Holo Pundits", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.holopundits.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "879473995923081"}], "external_subscription_type": "REQUIRED_FOR_SOME_CONTENT", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "6596900520434534"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982656_3601821450080